title: [Ta'Illistim, Linsandrych Var]
description: Beautiful white roses adorn a natural wall that lines one side of the cobblestone var, alabaster columns rising up from the verdant foliage.  A smooth marble walkway splits the hedge, leading to a domed rotunda.  Opposite the thick greenery is a wrought-iron fence, which allows a view of a well-tended garden beyond its bars.
